'''Android One'''是运行[[Android|Android]]系统的[[消费电子产品|消费电子产品]]系列。这是由[[Google|Google]]開發的搭载原生[[Android|Android]]系统的设备，市场面向[[发展中国家|发展中国家]]的人们和客户的第一个智能手机。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://stocknewsdesk.com/led-google-android-launch-1217225.html|title=What led to Google Android One launch?|date=September 16, 2014|publisher=StockNewsDesk|access-date=2015-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922103659/http://stocknewsdesk.com/led-google-android-launch-1217225.html|archive-date=2014-09-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[Google|Google]]负责设计、开发、营销和支持这些设备，原始设备制造商（OEM）负责制造。Android One[[智能手机|智能手机]]运行Android原生系统，没有经过制造商的定制，因此许多智能手机厂商申请加入。由Google负责安全性和系统更新，避免手机出现问题以及缺乏安全更新。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/9/15/6151329/first-android-one-smartphones-announced |title=Google reveals the first ultra-cheap Android One smartphones |accessdate=2015-08-14 |archive-date=2015-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150805021756/http://www.theverge.com/2014/9/15/6151329/first-android-one-smartphones-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.zdnet.com/with-android-one-google-puts-itself-firmly-back-in-the-os-driving-seat-7000033662/ |title=With Android One, Google puts itself firmly back in the OS' driving seat |accessdate=2015-08-14 |archive-date=2014-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111174907/http://www.zdnet.com/with-android-one-google-puts-itself-firmly-back-in-the-os-driving-seat-7000033662/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>第一批的Android One设备特性包括[[联发科|联发科]]四核[[联发科#四核|MT6582]]移动芯片系统。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mediatek.com/en/news-events/mediatek-news/mediatek-teams-with-google-on-android-one-to-create-affordable-smartphones-for-emerging-markets/ |title=MediaTek Teams With Google on Android One™ to Create Affordable Smartphones for Emerging Markets |accessdate=2015-08-14 |archive-date=2014-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140919005936/http://www.mediatek.com/en/news-events/mediatek-news/mediatek-teams-with-google-on-android-one-to-create-affordable-smartphones-for-emerging-markets/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

各种新闻文章提到了Android One设备还规定了最低硬件要求标准，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tech.firstpost.com/news-analysis/android-one-launches-in-india-why-googles-latest-project-is-a-big-deal-233891.html |title=Android One launches in India: Why Google’s latest project is a big deal |accessdate=2015-08-14 |archive-date=2015-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150731214526/http://tech.firstpost.com/news-analysis/android-one-launches-in-india-why-googles-latest-project-is-a-big-deal-233891.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.technotification.com/2014/09/google-gives-out-low-cost-android-one.html |title=Google Gives Out Low-Cost Android One |accessdate=2015-08-14 |archive-date=2015-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825083959/http://www.technotification.com/2014/09/google-gives-out-low-cost-android-one.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>但在互联网并没有曝光真实的最低要求。

== 历史 ==
{{Cquote|这是我们所做的产品中发布范围最广的一个，它包含任何地方，不仅限于印度、菲律宾和印度尼西亚。对我们来说，Android One还有漫长的旅程，它未来要获得十亿用户。而十亿用户中印度占的份额很大一部分，其中还附带'''[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]'''的自由边境贸易。研究结果发现，近7成产于印度的Android设备都被从尼泊尔赶来的用户购买。Android One设想与印度一样深深印在我的脑海中。|2014年NDTV采访Sundar Pichai|<ref name="gadgets.ndtv.com">http://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/googles-sundar-pichai-on-android-one-in-an-exclusive-chat-with-ndtvs-vikram-chandra-592062</ref>}}
Android One由Google-{高}-级副总裁[[Sundar_Pichai|Sundar Pichai]]推动。他倡议成立了印度市场的基本标准。<ref name="gadgets.ndtv.com"/>他还表示说，他很长一段时间内一直在使用Android One设备，将Android One作为他的“主要”设备。在各种意义上这是一个“高端计算设备”。{{cquote|我们推动Android One使它拥有一个完美的软件体验和一部完美的设备。我们十分的想吸引一些以前从来没有尝试过智能手机的人。 |Sundar Pichai||}}他还指出，因为它们所基于的基准平台，最初发布的设备有着共同的硬件。因为Google扩展了这个计划，设备将在今后陆续推出。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/googles-sundar-pichai-on-android-one-in-an-exclusive-chat-with-ndtvs-vikram-chandra-592062|title = NDTV Gadgets|date = 2014-07-15|accessdate = 2014-12-15|website = Android One Was Conceived With India in Mind, Says Google's Sundar Pichai|publisher = NDTV Correspondent|last = |first = |archive-date = 2014-11-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141117224055/http://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/googles-sundar-pichai-on-android-one-in-an-exclusive-chat-with-ndtvs-vikram-chandra-592062|dead-url = no}}</ref>

在2014年，Android One手机最初向[[印度|印度]]、[[孟加拉|孟加拉]]、[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://np.lifestohack.com/google-officially-launches-android-one-smartphones-in-nepal/ |title=Google officially launches Android One Smartphones in Nepal |access-date=2015-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141228173506/http://np.lifestohack.com/google-officially-launches-android-one-smartphones-in-nepal/ |archive-date=2014-12-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[印尼|印尼]]、[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]、[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]和其他南亚国家推出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnet.com/news/android-one-googles-push-to-rule-the-smartphone-world/ |title=Android One: Google's push to rule the smartphone world |accessdate=2015-08-14 |archive-date=2014-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140917010226/http://www.cnet.com/news/android-one-googles-push-to-rule-the-smartphone-world/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>第一批Android One智能手机是由印度品牌[[Micromax|Micromax]]、[[Spice|Spice]]和[[Karbonn|Karbonn]]在2014年9月推出，其他制造商如[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]的[[QMobile|QMobile]]在2015年7月6日推出了名为[[QMobile_A1|QMobile A1]]的Android One设备<ref>[http://www.qmobile.com.pk/phone-androidone.html/Google official Partner in Pakistan for Android One]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。其他生产商亦加入Android One。

2017年起，Google調整產品策略，將Android One提升為中階手機產品，原本針對開發中國家市場的入門產品改為[[Android_Go|Android Go]]。

常見的機型有[[小米A1|小米A1]]、[[小米A2|小米A2]]、[[Motorola_One|Motorola One]]、[[Motorola_One_Power|Motorola One Power]]、[[HTC_U11_life|HTC U11 life]]、[[Nokia_8.1|Nokia 8.1]]、[[Nokia_7_plus|Nokia 7 plus]]、[[Nokia_8_Sirocco|Nokia 8 Sirocco]]、[[Nokia_6.1|Nokia 6.1]]、[[Nokia_6.1_Plus|Nokia 6.1 Plus]]、[[Nokia_5.1_Plus|Nokia 5.1 Plus]]、[[Nokia_3.1_Plus|Nokia 3.1 Plus]]、[[Nokia_G50_5G|Nokia G50 5G]]、[[LG_G7_One|LG G7 One]]等等。

